{"tid":2237093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12義士家人請向護警會投訴有警察疑放生、協助中國公安拘捕香港人","createTime":"2020-10-10T03:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T09:23:07.000Z","uid":230104,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6396485750d5e78c4570e96168dec2f5d152b815","tid":2237093,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T03:55:48.000Z","msg":"雖然護警會一定是護警，但如果call齊記者高調向護警會/投訴警察課投訴，輿論會向佢哋施壓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩條罪，開邊邊都有罪：<br />\n1）警察當晚知情，但放生&lsquo;疑犯&rsquo;，即協助&lsquo;逃犯&rsquo;，咁理應唔止拉今日果9人，應拉埋當晚同樣協助&lsquo;疑犯&rsquo;的警察人員<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2）警察當晚知情，但協助中國公安拘捕，更大罪"},{"pid":"b05e1728748e10353634ba5afc77e7478f72fbc8","tid":2237093,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:03:09.000Z","msg":"重點係攬炒監警會主席<br />\n監警會主席梁定邦有大量支持警暴言論<br />\n梁定邦支持警察隱藏身份鎮壓示威<strong>以致大量女生遭私刑與強姦</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2110769/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2110769/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"8dc80ecfad01428b0128bf815c9090b75d2ccc85","tid":2237093,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:05:40.000Z","msg":"梁定邦條共狗一定偏幫警魔<br />\n第時一call條友發言紀錄就可以郁牌再囚終生,簡化審案過程<br />\n<br />\n若排期中條死撚樣爆血管仆街死咪益左條友"},{"pid":"0db7d4b708f54da813c7505df9945b252bca5f31","tid":2237093,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:20:31.000Z","msg":"又踢爆人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23519cbc45f99b161663d0551eccdab59a3be0bf","tid":2237093,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:48:53.000Z","msg":"如果今日被拉果9人有罪，理應有多名飛行服務隊員都要拉"},{"pid":"8e7fd6f51ca6f6dee6fd25b40a8f3f618b157456","tid":2237093,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:23:07.000Z","msg":"推"}]}